Source: sky1-firmware
Section: non-free-firmware/kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Entrpi <entrpi@proton.me>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13)
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/Sky1-Linux/sky1-firmware

Package: sky1-firmware
Architecture: all
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: Firmware and hardware config for CIX Sky1 SoC
 This package contains proprietary firmware and hardware configuration
 required for CIX Sky1 hardware:
 .
  - GPU: Mali-G720 CSF firmware (mali_csffw.bin)
  - DSP: Tensilica HiFi5 audio DSP firmware (dsp_fw.bin)
  - VPU: Video codec firmware (AV1, HEVC, H.264, VP9, etc.)
  - WiFi: Realtek RTL8852BE (rtw89)
  - Audio: ALSA UCM2 config for HDMI/DisplayPort audio
 .
 These files are required for GPU acceleration, audio DSP,
 hardware video encoding/decoding, WiFi, and HDMI audio on
 Radxa Orion O6 and compatible Sky1-based boards.
